{% extends 'layout.epy' %}
{% load widget_tweaks %}

{% block content %}
<div class="container about">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <h4>
        <p>
        Scoryst is a service started by Stanford University students to help make grading easier for instructors and grades more meaningful to students.
        </p>
        <p>
        Grading takes way too long. Add to that the hassle
        of sorting the exams, uploading scores, regrades and you wonder why this precious time
        couldn't be used for office hours instead.
        Students hate it too, especially when the exams are graded right before winter or spring break and the exams are never returned to them. What's the point in taking exams if they can't learn from their mistakes? Scoryst takes care of it.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <h3>Set</h3>
            <p>Upload your solutions and grading rubrics.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Scan</h3>
            <p>Scan all the student exams. Sounds intimidating? Don't worry, we'll take care of it
            for you!</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <h3>Grade</h3>
            With a beautiful, easy to use interface, finish grading in no time! You can even grade
            remotely instead of sitting in the office room all night. Students will then be emailed that their exams have been graded and they can see exactly where they lost points. Everybody wins.
          </li>
        </ul>
        </h4>
      
      <br />
