            Catherine is a senior majoring in Computer Science in the biocomputation track and doing her masters in Artificial Intelligence. She's a section leader for the introductory CS classes at Stanford and also interested in health, having served previously as the President of TeamHBV at Stanford. She can be seen playing with her corgi, Davy Lu  in her free time. 
